    * Fix crash in im-acquire-text with selection

  - uim-pref-qt4
    * Fix build failure when --as-needed is used (#40385, Julian Taylor)

* Enhancements
  - Qt4 bridge
    * Support text acquisition API with QTextEdit

* Others
